:''This is a list of biological virus families and subfamilies. See also [[Comparison of computer viruses]]''
This is an alphabetical list of biological [[virus]] families and subfamilies; it includes those families and subfamilies listed by the [[International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses|ICTV]] 2018 report.<ref name="ICTV">{{cite web |title=ICTV Master Species List 2018a v1 |url=https://talk.ictvonline.org/files/master-species-lists/m/msl/7992 |website=International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses (ICTV) |accessdate=27 November 2018 |location=Washington, DC |language=English |format=XLSX |date=July 2018}}</ref>
*For a list of individual species, see [[List of virus species]]. *For a list of virus genera, see [[List of genera of viruses]]. * For a list of virus realms, subrealms, kingdoms, subkingdoms, phyla, subphyla, classes, subclasses, orders, and suborders, see [[List of higher viral taxa]]. *For a taxonomic list, see [[Taxonomic list of viruses]].
